Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.38,0:00:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the greatest scandal since the\Nformation of the Czech police.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.67,0:00:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Much to our regret, the three that were murdered...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.09,0:00:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all had ties with the former Czechoslovakian\Nsecret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I would like to believe\Nthat because of this incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,any corruption within the Prague police\Ndepartment has been wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.23,0:00:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are all proud members of the Czech police.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.77,0:00:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I expect that you will act according to your conscience.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.61,0:00:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.40,0:00:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as the new Chief of Police...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.41,0:00:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will try hard to regain the trust of the people...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.32,0:00:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by carrying out a thorough reform.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.29,0:00:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NI will now introduce the five members of the special \N investigative task force from headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.29,0:00:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NI would like all of you to make a concerted effort...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.46,0:00:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to join them in solving this awful\Ncase as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.93,0:00:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Detective Suk, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.80,0:00:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.18,0:00:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the new Chief of Police, I would like to thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.56,0:00:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the investigative work you've done on this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.98,0:01:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.27,0:01:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what case are you assigned to right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.94,0:01:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one that Inspector Zeman was assigned to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.11,0:01:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It involves the murder of Mr. Petrov, the proprietor\Nof an unauthorized orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.57,0:01:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.87,0:01:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please continue to devote your efforts to that case.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.08,0:01:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.08,0:01:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.08,0:01:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.54,0:01:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding the tall man who emerged as a\Nsuspect in Inspector Zeman's murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.38,0:01:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know anything with regard to this suspect?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.51,0:01:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I know nothing about that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.72,0:01:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.02,0:01:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.48,0:01:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.07,0:01:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jan Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.78,0:01:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a year since he was assigned\Nto the Prague station.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been close to Inspector Zeman\Never since he started out...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.33,0:02:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He uncovered both Detective Patera's\Nand Detective Janacek's hidden past...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.63,0:02:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and met with Chief of Police \NHamrik right before his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put a tail on that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:55.55,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(392,0)\pos(324,357)}The Afterimage of the Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was glad when I called the hotel\Nyou said you were staying at...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.63,0:04:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you actually answered the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.93,0:04:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think you'd be betrayed again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.06,0:04:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orange juice, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.15,0:04:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you wanted to meet in a crowded place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but is it really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.99,0:04:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The new Chief of Police hasn't taken you off the\Nsuspect list for Inspector Zeman's murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, you're being pursued by the former \N Czechoslovakian secret police as well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.37,0:04:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I suppose you're actually safer in crowded places...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no safe place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.09,0:05:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they want to get me, they can. Any time, any place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from that window with the red curtains.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Grimmer, just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.91,0:05:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just an unsuccessful journalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, why are you going through all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I might've gotten too involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't something to laugh about!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your life is in danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got involved because I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suk is currently at a cafe in Republic Square.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.81,0:05:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's meeting with that tall man, as we suspected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:05:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Grimmer, without a doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.53,0:06:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we let them hang out a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this all happened to you while\Nyou were investigating Petrov...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who was conducting brainwashing experiments\Non children when he was in East Germany?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.21,0:06:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And right before his death...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Retrov entrusted you with that\Nkey to a safety deposit box.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He also said something about the\Ndevelopment of a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The development of a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems there are many people who\Nwant to get their hands on that data.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The former secret police?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As well as that blonde woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The children at the orphanage also mentioned her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pretty blonde woman who left the house\Nright after Petrov was assassinated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea who she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't the slightest idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.22,0:07:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hid the fact that you're meeting me\Nlike this from your superiors, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay to betray the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really hiding anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is within my discretion as part of an investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.28,0:07:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I have thoroughly investigated the matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.12,0:07:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I intend to report it to the higher authorities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do a good job, I can also prove your innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look to your left too quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man under the umbrella to\Nyour left, reading a newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:07:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The secret police...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.03,0:08:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brought it with you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.69,0:08:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The key to the safety deposit box that I gave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.11,0:08:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to know, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who this monster is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.25,0:08:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it may be better for us not to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.68,0:08:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just now, I saw that woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is anything wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:08:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.33,0:08:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must've imagined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suk is on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.67,0:09:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to follow him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Suk, from the Prague Police, who called earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.44,0:10:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to have kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.49,0:10:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where our safety deposit boxes are kept.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please check the contents of the box in that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.57,0:10:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Research papers and a cassette tape...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a tape recorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.25,0:11:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to play it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where is this place?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kinderheim 511.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.02,0:11:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A child's voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is your name?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My name is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Johan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.82,0:11:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My name is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.16,0:11:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Johan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is your last name?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.92,0:11:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let me ask you again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is your last name?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.34,0:11:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My name is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Otto.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My name is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.47,0:12:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hans.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.81,0:12:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My name is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thomas.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My name is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.73,0:12:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which one is your real name?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.19,0:12:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once upon a time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there lived a monster without a name.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The monster wanted a name so\Nbadly that he couldn't stand it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.95,0:12:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is that a story of some kind?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was waiting... for Anna.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who is Anna?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.79,0:12:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was waiting for Anna, while reading a picture book...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This boy was being interrogated after being drugged.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.64,0:12:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who is your father?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What about your mother?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.23,0:12:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think she's still alive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You are a very talented child.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.27,0:12:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you afraid of anything?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:13:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is it that you're most afraid of?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.99,0:13:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let me change the question, then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Have you ever killed anyone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A lot of people were dead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was like Anna and I were the\N\Nonly ones left in the world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where was that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.63,0:13:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then, let's go back to the other question.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is it that you're most afraid of?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The monster inside of me is getting bigger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chomp chomp.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Munch munch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gulp.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chomp chomp.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Munch munch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.99,0:13:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gulp.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chomp chomp.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.62,0:13:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Munch munch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gulp.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.29,0:13:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What I am most afraid of...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.41,0:13:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.84,0:14:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'm going to throw up...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Mr. Grimmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.39,0:14:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what is this tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the monster's identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we don't understand the meaning of this tape...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there are people out there who'd do\Nanything to get their hands on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The former Czechoslovakian secret police...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.58,0:14:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you listen to only part of the tape or the\Nentire thing, it doesn't make any difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no turning back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to putt that tape and the research\Npapers back in the safety deposit box?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.23,0:15:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.57,0:15:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, they should be kept here as evidence, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.36,0:15:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to hang on to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's leave here separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably me they're targeting anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.92,0:15:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your cell phone number and your home address.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.84,0:15:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're both safe, let's contact each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.42,0:16:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I made it home safely...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bad feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.24,0:16:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems to be unreliable after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.24,0:16:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A flat on Lenova Street...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.04,0:16:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we'd like to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know about us, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're with that special task force\Nthat headquarters sent over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.89,0:16:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Senior Detective Novacek.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:17:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Senior Detective Janda.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why are you both in my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.61,0:17:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long have you been meeting with Grimmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't say you don't know what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just now, you met him at a cafe in Republic Square...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then you guys headed to Proch{\fnMeiryo U}á{\fnNarkisim}zka Bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.12,0:17:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the man in this picture, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel Karel Ranke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a big shot in the underground\NCzechoslovakian secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I don't know that person!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We checked your bank account.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There seems to have been a large\Nsum deposited this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.89,0:17:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything about that money
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother is currently hospitalized for a serious\Nillness at Krumlov National Hospital, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.86,0:17:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that it costs a lot just to pay\Nfor her hospitalization, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:17:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After your mother separated from your father...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she raised you all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And apparently, you care a lot about your mother as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.96,0:18:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what are you trying to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We would like to search your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.85,0:18:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing to hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:18:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Janda, come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.62,0:19:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were in your medicine cabinet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,0:19:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know nothing about them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't say anything about the chemical content\Nuntil we analyze them at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.42,0:19:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the stomachs of the three that were murdered...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.88,0:19:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the items they found that contained\Nthe muscle relaxant...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.51,0:19:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were whisky bonbons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hear your story back at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Investigate it thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.49,0:19:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:20:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But before that, could I at least change first?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.54,0:20:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.67,0:20:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll understand if I explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.98,0:20:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The smell of gunpowder...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suk!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.89,0:22:31.06,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.06,0:22:44.49,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,475)}Cherish what you know is true in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.06,0:22:44.49,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(201,21)}Ima kono sekai de wakaru koto mitsumete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.49,0:22:47.45,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(182,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.45,0:23:01.13,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(198,472)}Please believe in the kindness of your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.45,0:23:01.13,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,21)}Anata no hitomi no yasashisa wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.73,0:23:25.99,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(196,473)}Make it home to your land of harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.99,0:23:34.41,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(195,473)}Make it home to your land of purity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.41,0:23:36.87,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,246)\pos(187,472)}Make it home
